Title: Nielsen-Olesen vortices in noncommutative space
Authors: G.S. Lozano, E.F. Moreno and F.A. Schaposnik
Comments: 9 pages, 1 figure, typos corrected, one reference added. To appear in
  Phys. Lett. B
Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B504 (2001) 117-121
\\
  We construct an exact regular vortex solution to the self-dual equations of
the Abelian Higgs model in non-commutative space for arbitrary values of
$\theta$. To this end, we propose an ansatz which is the analogous, in Fock
space, to the one leading to exact solutions for the Nielsen-Olesen vortex in
commutative space. We compute the flux and energy of the solution and discuss
its relevant properties.
